The '''''Winning Hand''''' was a pleasure ship the size of a medium transport. In [[26 ABY/Legends|26 ABY]], it made a [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]] jump from the [[Corellian sector/Legends|Corellian sector]] to the [[Meridian sector/Legends|Meridian sector]], near [[Obroa-skai/Legends|Obroa-skai]] along the [[Perlemian Trade Route/Legends|Perlemian Trade Route]], and vanished after making a garbled transmission. It was located by [[Uldir Lochett]] aboard the ''[[Pride of Thela]]''.

However, it was revealed to be a [[Peace Brigade]] ship, and unsuccessfully attempted to capture the ''Pride of Thela'' with its [[Tractor beam/Legends|tractor beams]].

